# User Authentication Endpoints

### Register a new user
POST http://localhost:3030/api/auth/register 
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "john@example.com",
    "password": "password123",
    "firstName": "John",
    "lastName": "Doe",
    "location": "New York",
    "dob": "1990-01-01",
    "ssn": "123-45-678",
    "visaCardNumber": "1234-5678-9012-3456",
    "visaExpiry": "12/2025",
    "visaCW": "123"
}

### Login an existing user
POST http://localhost:3030/api/auth/login 
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "john@example.com",
    "password": "password123"
}

### Get the current user (requires authentication)
GET http://localhost:3030/api/auth/me 
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6IjY4MTQwNTM0MDE4MGViYWY0ZGY3NWRlYiIsImlhdCI6MTc0Njg4OTYwMywiZXhwIjoxNzQ5NDgxNjAzfQ.WUWW8CuYMJyUTl_W0bVuPCkN8rj0MeXTzRpYQu9rKss

